  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> and finely slice 3 rings per person, then dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>red onion rings</strong> and your<strong> red wine vinegar </strong>to a shallow bowl and set aside to pickle until serving – these are your <strong>quick-pickled red onion rings</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
