    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine your <strong>vegan mayo </strong>with 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp</span>] <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>herby mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
