            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then separate the <strong>outer leaves </strong>and shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Drain and finely dice your <strong>pineapple slices</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> diced pineapple </strong>and your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) in a bowl with plenty of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
